    <item>
      <title>特朗普竞选团队 8 月份支出比筹集的资金多 3200 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-campaign-spent-32-million-more-than-it-raised-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统竞选进入迄今为止最激烈、最昂贵的阶段，唐纳德·特朗普动用了自己的竞选资金，试图阻止民主党对手卡马拉·哈里斯的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-campaign-spent-32-million-more-than-it-raised-in-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 20:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 筹款闪电战由加密货币支持者发起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kamala-harris-fundraising-blitz-in-works-by-supporters-in-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的加密行业支持者正在努力在未来几周内建立至少八次筹款活动，以造福民主党候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kamala-harris-fundraising-blitz-in-works-by-supporters-in-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 20:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯向 100 万美元收入者征收 28% 的资本利得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/harris-to-push-capital-gains-tax-rate-below-39-6-bucking-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯呼吁对收入 100 万美元或以上的人征收 28% 的资本利得税，称这是一项确保富人支付公平份额的措施，她试图详细说明她的经济议程并与共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普形成对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/harris-to-push-capital-gains-tax-rate-below-39-6-bucking-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将阻止新日铁收购美国钢铁公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/biden-to-block-nippon-steel-us-steel-deal-washington-post-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国总统拜登正准备阻止新日本制铁公司以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/biden-to-block-nippon-steel-us-steel-deal-washington-post-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:59:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基任命西比哈为乌克兰最高外交官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/zelenskiy-to-nominate-sybiha-as-foreign-minister-in-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基将提名高级外交官、前驻土耳其大使安德烈·西比哈 (Andrii Sybiha) 担任外交部长，这是自 2022 年俄罗斯入侵以来最大规模内阁改组的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/zelenskiy-to-nominate-sybiha-as-foreign-minister-in-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:49:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称克里姆林宫支持的干预选举阴谋已被挫败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-accuses-russian-backed-entities-of-2024-election-meddling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府在宣布采取措施阻止该计划时指控称，俄罗斯支持的实体进行了长达数年的大规模行动，以干预 2024 年美国总统大选并广泛提升克里姆林宫的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-accuses-russian-backed-entities-of-2024-election-meddling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多失去关键盟友，加拿大提前大选概率增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/canada-s-ndp-pulls-out-of-deal-propping-up-trudeau-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[让加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的自由党继续执政的议会协议已经破裂，这增加了近期举行大选的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/canada-s-ndp-pulls-out-of-deal-propping-up-trudeau-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:54:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Steward 首席执行官在破产程序结束前不会在参议院作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/steward-ceo-refuses-to-testify-in-senate-until-bankruptcy-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯图尔特医疗集团 (Steward Health Care) 首席执行官拉尔夫·德拉托雷 (Ralph de La Torre) 告知参议员，在医院破产程序结束之前，他不会参加即将举行的调查医院运营商失败的听证会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/steward-ceo-refuses-to-testify-in-senate-until-bankruptcy-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 15:36:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国移民法庭，正义并不是重点。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/tribunales-inmigracion-eeuu-en-manos-de-politica-y-le-falla-a-solicitantes-asilo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[决定庇护案件的系统正在失败，不仅仅是因为它不堪重负。必须采取一些重大措施来修复存在根本缺陷的流程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/tribunales-inmigracion-eeuu-en-manos-de-politica-y-le-falla-a-solicitantes-asilo</guid>
